title: The Women's March Organizers Announce A "General Strike" For "A Day Without A Woman"
text:
The Women's March Organizers Announce A "General Strike" For "A Day Without A Woman" Source: Michael Loccisano/Getty Images Entertainment/Getty Images By Natasha Guzmán a min ago 
Keeping their promise that the Women's March on Washington would continue to be a movement rather than just a moment, the protest's organizers have announced a general strike. The will of the people will stand. pic.twitter.com/SKJCRLhRKn
